channel.title: [Contest] Giving away 5 RS accounts
channel.description:
[center][size=20pt][b]Runescape account giveaway[/b][/size] [/center] Rules of this contest:
[ul][li]You may only guess 1 number.[/li] [li]You may not make multiple accounts. (It's against the rules anyway.)[/li][/ul]
Simply guess a number from 1 to 40. I will draw 5 winners using [url=http://www.random.org/]http://www.random.org/[/url]
Once the winners are picked, I will do another randomization from 1 to 5, to see who gets which account.
[u][b]Account #1:[/b][/u] Combat level: 43 Quest points: 14 Estimated money on account: 140K [img]http://i.imgur.com/EsIlp.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/1j8L7.png[/img]
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[u][b]Account #3:[/b][/u] Combat level: 70 Quest points: 54 Estimated money on account: 160K [img]http://i.imgur.com/ArJeJ.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/2glqC.png[/img]
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[u][b]Account #4:[/b][/u] Combat level: 33 Quest points: 7 Estimated money on account: 15K [img]http://i.imgur.com/cFJka.png[/img]
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[u][b]Account #5:[/b][/u] Combat level: 56 Quest points: 36 Estimated money on account: 10K [img]http://i.imgur.com/fq63G.png[/img]
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note: These accounts haven't been active for two years, did not bot these, they were hand trained. This is the first time logging into them in two years.
I wish you guys all luck. When all 40 entries have been filled in, the contest will end and the winners will be selected.
Entries:
